## Requirements:

NodeJS >= v18.14.1
NPM >= v9.3.1

## Project Setup (Run all the comands below on the project root directory)

> - Run the following command to install the dependencies
>   _npm install_
>
> - Configure .env file by duplicating .env.example file and rename it to .env \
>
> - Setup Lucid ORM
>   _node ace configure @adonisjs/lucid_
>   Use SQLite since it's already configured. You may change this just follow the documentation
>
> - Run the following command to create the database tables (database used is sqlite)
>   _node ace migration:fresh_
>
> - Run the following command to start the server in developement
>   _node ace serve_

## Alternative

- Run the custom npm script:

> - _npm run setup_
>
>   - select SQLite
>
> - _npm run dev_
